立法會主席曾鈺成 家人(加拿大藉)<br />\n前民政事務局長劉江華 (家屬已移民加拿大)<br />\n港大校委會主席李國章 (嫁鬼婆生鬼仔)<br />\n前創新及科技局長楊偉雄 (家屬美籍) 在美國有5個物業<br />\n前教育局長吳克儉 子女(外國升學,已入籍)<br />\n前商務及經濟發展局長蘇錦樑 (加拿大藉)<br />\n前民政事務局長曾德成的子女 (外國升學)<br />\n譚志源兩子 (在國際學校就讀)<br />\n愛黨藍絲周融 (大英帝國公民)<br />\n愛國導演高智森 (95年全家移民美國)....<br />\n.... 太多不能盡錄"},{"pid":"ea10a5e36be75cddb99092b2da07f18869753fb7","tid":2421241,"uid":229777,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c04740f2d99efcffbd55edc704c624a9608a6fd1","tid":2421241,"uid":30067,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T22:03:59.000Z","msg":"中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T22:12:08.000Z","msg":"又有一個中國人？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6c029756a959f5a78c0dcf018441783378b689","tid":2421241,"uid":389177,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T22:18:53.000Z","msg":"中国。"},{"pid":"79ad4b925e1eb9bd72613ccbb0536cb0e8b84d7a","tid":2421241,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"ea10a5e36be75cddb99092b2da07f18869753fb7","tid":2421241,"uid":229777,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c04740f2d99efcffbd55edc704c624a9608a6fd1","tid":2421241,"uid":30067,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T22:03:59.000Z","msg":"中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T22:12:08.000Z","msg":"又有一個中國人？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T22:18:56.000Z","msg":"冇計<br />\n雖然老豆老母都係香港出世香港大<br />\n但係<br />\n我阿爺個老豆係中國出世中國長大<br />\n我阿麻個老豆係中國出世馬來西亞長大<br />\n我阿公係中國出世<br />\n我阿婆個老豆係中國出世中國長大<br />\n睇來我都係100%支那種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c272b27d66e3f0875fa7ab2120913ede6389b4d","tid":2421241,"uid":265338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"97f44ae6db054ae3c252d4a25948094d96b116c6","tid":2421241,"uid":2